details.description: This gear comes with a 150-pound selectorized weight stack that can be customized according to your skill level to avoid the stresses of loading and unloading weight plates with a safety lock that prevents unauthorized use of equipment

The PharMeDoc Abdominal Wheel Ab Roller wheel helps you get a complete ab workout to help you build stronger and more chiseled six pack abs, obliques, hip flexors, legs, shoulders, chest, and triceps, making this a must-have piece of home exercise equipment for abdominal muscles.

This gear comes with a 150-pound selectorized weight stack that can be customized according to your skill level to avoid the stresses of loading and unloading weight plates with a safety lock that prevents unauthorized use of equipment
